title: Host Fulton sweeps Amboy
text:
Host Fulton sweeps Amboy 
FULTON, Ill. â€” Fulton swept Amboy at home Thursday night with a 25-19, 25-20 win. 
Brooke Huizenga led the Steamers (17-10, 7-4 Three Rivers) with eight kills while Camerin Huizenga and Betsy Leonard had five kills apiece.
